description: Returns an array of resources associated with the specified web ACL.

parameters.name: WebACLId
parameters.description: The unique identifier (ID) of the web ACL for which to list the associated resources.

nested_items.name: ResourceArns
nested_items.description: An array of ARNs (Amazon Resource Names) of the resources associated with the specified web ACL. An array with zero elements is returned if there are no resources associated with the web ACL.
